      <title>为什么印度尼西亚的全面大修吓到市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/indonesia-stock-market-why-are-investors-fleeing-what-role-has-prabowo-played</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从10月，普拉博沃·苏不匹（Prabowo Subianto）总统上任以来，印度尼西亚的股票市场跌倒了，到3月下旬，卢比亚（Rupiah）自1997  -  1998年亚洲金融危机以来，卢比亚（Rupiah）跌至其最低水平，当时该国被国际货币基金救护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/indonesia-stock-market-why-are-investors-fleeing-what-role-has-prabowo-played</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 03:40:39 GMT</pubDate>
